{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":641,"text":"I would like to tell you a story"},{"time":2995,"text":"connecting the notorious privacy incident"},{"time":6171,"text":"involving Adam and Eve,"},{"time":8940,"text":"and the remarkable shift in the boundaries"},{"time":12386,"text":"between public and private which has occurred"},{"time":15072,"text":"in the past 10 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16842,"text":"You know the incident."},{"time":18140,"text":"Adam and Eve one day in the Garden of Eden"},{"time":21470,"text":"realize they are naked."},{"time":23313,"text":"They freak out."},{"time":24813,"text":"And the rest is history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27570,"text":"Nowadays, Adam and Eve"},{"time":29758,"text":"would probably act differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32119,"text":"[@Adam Last nite was a blast! loved dat apple LOL]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34387,"text":"[@Eve yep.. babe, know what happened to my pants tho?]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36260,"text":"We do reveal so much more information"},{"time":38896,"text":"about ourselves online than ever before,"},{"time":42230,"text":"and so much information about us"},{"time":43934,"text":"is being collected by organizations."},{"time":46158,"text":"Now there is much to gain and benefit"},{"time":49440,"text":"from this massive analysis of personal information,"},{"time":51886,"text":"or big data,"},{"time":53832,"text":"but there are also complex tradeoffs that come"},{"time":56470,"text":"from giving away our privacy."},{"time":59568,"text":"And my story is about these tradeoffs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63591,"text":"We start with an observation which, in my mind,"},{"time":66175,"text":"has become clearer and clearer in the past few years,"},{"time":69502,"text":"that any personal information"},{"time":71599,"text":"can become sensitive information."},{"time":73884,"text":"Back in the year 2000, about 100 billion photos"},{"time":78009,"text":"were shot worldwide,"},{"time":79921,"text":"but only a minuscule proportion of them"},{"time":82986,"text":"were actually uploaded online."},{"time":84869,"text":"In 2010, only on Facebook, in a single month,"},{"time":88230,"text":"2.5 billion photos were uploaded,"},{"time":91500,"text":"most of them identified."},{"time":93382,"text":"In the same span of time,"},{"time":95262,"text":"computers' ability to recognize people in photos"},{"time":100132,"text":"improved by three orders of magnitude."},{"time":103740,"text":"What happens when you combine"},{"time":105622,"text":"these technologies together:"},{"time":107123,"text":"increasing availability of facial data;"},{"time":109781,"text":"improving facial recognizing ability by computers;"},{"time":113429,"text":"but also cloud computing,"},{"time":115611,"text":"which gives anyone in this theater"},{"time":117499,"text":"the kind of computational power"},{"time":119059,"text":"which a few years ago was only the domain"},{"time":120945,"text":"of three-letter agencies;"},{"time":122727,"text":"and ubiquitous computing,"},{"time":124105,"text":"which allows my phone, which is not a supercomputer,"},{"time":126997,"text":"to connect to the Internet"},{"time":128668,"text":"and do there hundreds of thousands"},{"time":131002,"text":"of face metrics in a few seconds?"},{"time":133641,"text":"Well, we conjecture that the result"},{"time":136269,"text":"of this combination of technologies"},{"time":138333,"text":"will be a radical change in our very notions"},{"time":141221,"text":"of privacy and anonymity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143478,"text":"To test that, we did an experiment"},{"time":145471,"text":"on Carnegie Mellon University campus."},{"time":147592,"text":"We asked students who were walking by"},{"time":149691,"text":"to participate in a study,"},{"time":151470,"text":"and we took a shot with a webcam,"},{"time":154032,"text":"and we asked them to fill out a survey on a laptop."},{"time":156814,"text":"While they were filling out the survey,"},{"time":158793,"text":"we uploaded their shot to a cloud-computing cluster,"},{"time":161590,"text":"and we started using a facial recognizer"},{"time":163317,"text":"to match that shot to a database"},{"time":165722,"text":"of some hundreds of thousands of images"},{"time":168115,"text":"which we had downloaded from Facebook profiles."},{"time":171711,"text":"By the time the subject reached the last page"},{"time":174970,"text":"on the survey, the page had been dynamically updated"},{"time":178317,"text":"with the 10 best matching photos"},{"time":180630,"text":"which the recognizer had found,"},{"time":182915,"text":"and we asked the subjects to indicate"},{"time":184653,"text":"whether he or she found themselves in the photo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188773,"text":"Do you see the subject?"},{"time":192472,"text":"Well, the computer did, and in fact did so"},{"time":195317,"text":"for one out of three subjects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":197466,"text":"So essentially, we can start from an anonymous face,"},{"time":200650,"text":"offline or online, and we can use facial recognition"},{"time":204134,"text":"to give a name to that anonymous face"},{"time":206494,"text":"thanks to social media data."},{"time":208602,"text":"But a few years back, we did something else."},{"time":210474,"text":"We started from social media data,"},{"time":212297,"text":"we combined it statistically with data"},{"time":215348,"text":"from U.S. government social security,"},{"time":217450,"text":"and we ended up predicting social security numbers,"},{"time":220774,"text":"which in the United States"},{"time":222286,"text":"are extremely sensitive information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224326,"text":"Do you see where I'm going with this?"},{"time":226419,"text":"So if you combine the two studies together,"},{"time":229341,"text":"then the question becomes,"},{"time":230853,"text":"can you start from a face and,"},{"time":233573,"text":"using facial recognition, find a name"},{"time":235884,"text":"and publicly available information"},{"time":238553,"text":"about that name and that person,"},{"time":240485,"text":"and from that publicly available information"},{"time":242733,"text":"infer non-publicly available information,"},{"time":244775,"text":"much more sensitive ones"},{"time":246381,"text":"which you link back to the face?"},{"time":247873,"text":"And the answer is, yes, we can, and we did."},{"time":249789,"text":"Of course, the accuracy keeps getting worse."},{"time":252357,"text":"[27% of subjects' first 5 SSN digits identified (with 4 attempts)]"},{"time":253301,"text":"But in fact, we even decided to develop an iPhone app"},{"time":257128,"text":"which uses the phone's internal camera"},{"time":259843,"text":"to take a shot of a subject"},{"time":261443,"text":"and then upload it to a cloud"},{"time":262930,"text":"and then do what I just described to you in real time:"},{"time":265592,"text":"looking for a match, finding public information,"},{"time":267680,"text":"trying to infer sensitive information,"},{"time":269410,"text":"and then sending back to the phone"},{"time":272001,"text":"so that it is overlaid on the face of the subject,"},{"time":275610,"text":"an example of augmented reality,"},{"time":277511,"text":"probably a creepy example of augmented reality."},{"time":279962,"text":"In fact, we didn't develop the app to make it available,"},{"time":283301,"text":"just as a proof of concept."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285223,"text":"In fact, take these technologies"},{"time":287536,"text":"and push them to their logical extreme."},{"time":289373,"text":"Imagine a future in which strangers around you"},{"time":292092,"text":"will look at you through their Google Glasses"},{"time":294403,"text":"or, one day, their contact lenses,"},{"time":296710,"text":"and use seven or eight data points about you"},{"time":300730,"text":"to infer anything else"},{"time":303312,"text":"which may be known about you."},{"time":305915,"text":"What will this future without secrets look like?"},{"time":310709,"text":"And should we care?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":312673,"text":"We may like to believe"},{"time":314564,"text":"that the future with so much wealth of data"},{"time":317604,"text":"would be a future with no more biases,"},{"time":320118,"text":"but in fact, having so much information"},{"time":323701,"text":"doesn't mean that we will make decisions"},{"time":325892,"text":"which are more objective."},{"time":327598,"text":"In another experiment, we presented to our subjects"},{"time":330158,"text":"information about a potential job candidate."},{"time":332404,"text":"We included in this information some references"},{"time":335582,"text":"to some funny, absolutely legal,"},{"time":338228,"text":"but perhaps slightly embarrassing information"},{"time":340693,"text":"that the subject had posted online."},{"time":342713,"text":"Now interestingly, among our subjects,"},{"time":345079,"text":"some had posted comparable information,"},{"time":348162,"text":"and some had not."},{"time":350524,"text":"Which group do you think"},{"time":352473,"text":"was more likely to judge harshly our subject?"},{"time":357025,"text":"Paradoxically, it was the group"},{"time":358982,"text":"who had posted similar information,"},{"time":360715,"text":"an example of moral dissonance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363657,"text":"Now you may be thinking,"},{"time":365407,"text":"this does not apply to me,"},{"time":367109,"text":"because I have nothing to hide."},{"time":369271,"text":"But in fact, privacy is not about"},{"time":371753,"text":"having something negative to hide."},{"time":375429,"text":"Imagine that you are the H.R. director"},{"time":377783,"text":"of a certain organization, and you receive résumés,"},{"time":380730,"text":"and you decide to find more information about the candidates."},{"time":383203,"text":"Therefore, you Google their names"},{"time":385663,"text":"and in a certain universe,"},{"time":387903,"text":"you find this information."},{"time":389911,"text":"Or in a parallel universe, you find this information."},{"time":394348,"text":"Do you think that you would be equally likely"},{"time":397065,"text":"to call either candidate for an interview?"},{"time":399868,"text":"If you think so, then you are not"},{"time":402150,"text":"like the U.S. employers who are, in fact,"},{"time":404732,"text":"part of our experiment, meaning we did exactly that."},{"time":408039,"text":"We created Facebook profiles, manipulating traits,"},{"time":411221,"text":"then we started sending out résumés to companies in the U.S.,"},{"time":414072,"text":"and we detected, we monitored,"},{"time":415980,"text":"whether they were searching for our candidates,"},{"time":418373,"text":"and whether they were acting on the information"},{"time":420205,"text":"they found on social media. And they were."},{"time":422143,"text":"Discrimination was happening through social media"},{"time":424244,"text":"for equally skilled candidates."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427317,"text":"Now marketers like us to believe"},{"time":431892,"text":"that all information about us will always"},{"time":434161,"text":"be used in a manner which is in our favor."},{"time":437434,"text":"But think again. Why should that be always the case?"},{"time":441149,"text":"In a movie which came out a few years ago,"},{"time":443813,"text":"\"Minority Report,\" a famous scene"},{"time":446366,"text":"had Tom Cruise walk in a mall"},{"time":448942,"text":"and holographic personalized advertising"},{"time":452718,"text":"would appear around him."},{"time":454553,"text":"Now, that movie is set in 2054,"},{"time":457780,"text":"about 40 years from now,"},{"time":459422,"text":"and as exciting as that technology looks,"},{"time":462330,"text":"it already vastly underestimates"},{"time":464976,"text":"the amount of information that organizations"},{"time":467116,"text":"can gather about you, and how they can use it"},{"time":469599,"text":"to influence you in a way that you will not even detect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472997,"text":"So as an example, this is another experiment"},{"time":475100,"text":"actually we are running, not yet completed."},{"time":477373,"text":"Imagine that an organization has access"},{"time":479692,"text":"to your list of Facebook friends,"},{"time":481748,"text":"and through some kind of algorithm"},{"time":483520,"text":"they can detect the two friends that you like the most."},{"time":487254,"text":"And then they create, in real time,"},{"time":489534,"text":"a facial composite of these two friends."},{"time":492376,"text":"Now studies prior to ours have shown that people"},{"time":495445,"text":"don't recognize any longer even themselves"},{"time":498330,"text":"in facial composites, but they react"},{"time":500792,"text":"to those composites in a positive manner."},{"time":502909,"text":"So next time you are looking for a certain product,"},{"time":506324,"text":"and there is an ad suggesting you to buy it,"},{"time":508883,"text":"it will not be just a standard spokesperson."},{"time":511790,"text":"It will be one of your friends,"},{"time":514103,"text":"and you will not even know that this is happening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517406,"text":"Now the problem is that"},{"time":519819,"text":"the current policy mechanisms we have"},{"time":522338,"text":"to protect ourselves from the abuses of personal information"},{"time":525776,"text":"are like bringing a knife to a gunfight."},{"time":528760,"text":"One of these mechanisms is transparency,"},{"time":531673,"text":"telling people what you are going to do with their data."},{"time":534873,"text":"And in principle, that's a very good thing."},{"time":536979,"text":"It's necessary, but it is not sufficient."},{"time":540646,"text":"Transparency can be misdirected."},{"time":544344,"text":"You can tell people what you are going to do,"},{"time":546448,"text":"and then you still nudge them to disclose"},{"time":548680,"text":"arbitrary amounts of personal information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":551303,"text":"So in yet another experiment, this one with students,"},{"time":554189,"text":"we asked them to provide information"},{"time":557247,"text":"about their campus behavior,"},{"time":559060,"text":"including pretty sensitive questions, such as this one."},{"time":562000,"text":"[Have you ever cheated in an exam?]"},{"time":562621,"text":"Now to one group of subjects, we told them,"},{"time":564921,"text":"\"Only other students will see your answers.\""},{"time":567762,"text":"To another group of subjects, we told them,"},{"time":569341,"text":"\"Students and faculty will see your answers.\""},{"time":572902,"text":"Transparency. Notification. And sure enough, this worked,"},{"time":575493,"text":"in the sense that the first group of subjects"},{"time":576900,"text":"were much more likely to disclose than the second."},{"time":579468,"text":"It makes sense, right?"},{"time":580988,"text":"But then we added the misdirection."},{"time":582478,"text":"We repeated the experiment with the same two groups,"},{"time":585238,"text":"this time adding a delay"},{"time":587665,"text":"between the time we told subjects"},{"time":590600,"text":"how we would use their data"},{"time":592680,"text":"and the time we actually started answering the questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597068,"text":"How long a delay do you think we had to add"},{"time":599629,"text":"in order to nullify the inhibitory effect"},{"time":604242,"text":"of knowing that faculty would see your answers?"},{"time":607653,"text":"Ten minutes?"},{"time":609433,"text":"Five minutes?"},{"time":611224,"text":"One minute?"},{"time":613000,"text":"How about 15 seconds?"},{"time":615049,"text":"Fifteen seconds were sufficient to have the two groups"},{"time":617717,"text":"disclose the same amount of information,"},{"time":619285,"text":"as if the second group now no longer cares"},{"time":622031,"text":"for faculty reading their answers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624687,"text":"Now I have to admit that this talk so far"},{"time":628023,"text":"may sound exceedingly gloomy,"},{"time":630503,"text":"but that is not my point."},{"time":632224,"text":"In fact, I want to share with you the fact that"},{"time":634923,"text":"there are alternatives."},{"time":636695,"text":"The way we are doing things now is not the only way"},{"time":639194,"text":"they can done, and certainly not the best way"},{"time":642231,"text":"they can be done."},{"time":644258,"text":"When someone tells you, \"People don't care about privacy,\""},{"time":648429,"text":"consider whether the game has been designed"},{"time":651071,"text":"and rigged so that they cannot care about privacy,"},{"time":653795,"text":"and coming to the realization that these manipulations occur"},{"time":657057,"text":"is already halfway through the process"},{"time":658664,"text":"of being able to protect yourself."},{"time":660922,"text":"When someone tells you that privacy is incompatible"},{"time":664632,"text":"with the benefits of big data,"},{"time":666481,"text":"consider that in the last 20 years,"},{"time":668954,"text":"researchers have created technologies"},{"time":670871,"text":"to allow virtually any electronic transactions"},{"time":674189,"text":"to take place in a more privacy-preserving manner."},{"time":677938,"text":"We can browse the Internet anonymously."},{"time":680493,"text":"We can send emails that can only be read"},{"time":683171,"text":"by the intended recipient, not even the NSA."},{"time":686880,"text":"We can have even privacy-preserving data mining."},{"time":689877,"text":"In other words, we can have the benefits of big data"},{"time":693771,"text":"while protecting privacy."},{"time":695903,"text":"Of course, these technologies imply a shifting"},{"time":699694,"text":"of cost and revenues"},{"time":701240,"text":"between data holders and data subjects,"},{"time":703347,"text":"which is why, perhaps, you don't hear more about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706800,"text":"Which brings me back to the Garden of Eden."},{"time":710506,"text":"There is a second privacy interpretation"},{"time":713286,"text":"of the story of the Garden of Eden"},{"time":715095,"text":"which doesn't have to do with the issue"},{"time":717191,"text":"of Adam and Eve feeling naked"},{"time":719416,"text":"and feeling ashamed."},{"time":721797,"text":"You can find echoes of this interpretation"},{"time":724578,"text":"in John Milton's \"Paradise Lost.\""},{"time":727360,"text":"In the garden, Adam and Eve are materially content."},{"time":731557,"text":"They're happy. They are satisfied."},{"time":733661,"text":"However, they also lack knowledge"},{"time":735954,"text":"and self-awareness."},{"time":737594,"text":"The moment they eat the aptly named"},{"time":740913,"text":"fruit of knowledge,"},{"time":742206,"text":"that's when they discover themselves."},{"time":744811,"text":"They become aware. They achieve autonomy."},{"time":748842,"text":"The price to pay, however, is leaving the garden."},{"time":751968,"text":"So privacy, in a way, is both the means"},{"time":755849,"text":"and the price to pay for freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":758811,"text":"Again, marketers tell us"},{"time":761581,"text":"that big data and social media"},{"time":764600,"text":"are not just a paradise of profit for them,"},{"time":767579,"text":"but a Garden of Eden for the rest of us."},{"time":770036,"text":"We get free content."},{"time":771274,"text":"We get to play Angry Birds. We get targeted apps."},{"time":774397,"text":"But in fact, in a few years, organizations"},{"time":777294,"text":"will know so much about us,"},{"time":778903,"text":"they will be able to infer our desires"},{"time":781613,"text":"before we even form them, and perhaps"},{"time":783817,"text":"buy products on our behalf"},{"time":786264,"text":"before we even know we need them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788538,"text":"Now there was one English author"},{"time":791775,"text":"who anticipated this kind of future"},{"time":794820,"text":"where we would trade away"},{"time":796225,"text":"our autonomy and freedom for comfort."},{"time":799773,"text":"Even more so than George Orwell,"},{"time":801934,"text":"the author is, of course, Aldous Huxley."},{"time":804695,"text":"In \"Brave New World,\" he imagines a society"},{"time":807549,"text":"where technologies that we created"},{"time":809720,"text":"originally for freedom"},{"time":811579,"text":"end up coercing us."},{"time":814146,"text":"However, in the book, he also offers us a way out"},{"time":818937,"text":"of that society, similar to the path"},{"time":822375,"text":"that Adam and Eve had to follow to leave the garden."},{"time":826330,"text":"In the words of the Savage,"},{"time":828477,"text":"regaining autonomy and freedom is possible,"},{"time":831546,"text":"although the price to pay is steep."},{"time":834225,"text":"So I do believe that one of the defining fights"},{"time":839940,"text":"of our times will be the fight"},{"time":842503,"text":"for the control over personal information,"},{"time":844890,"text":"the fight over whether big data will become a force"},{"time":848397,"text":"for freedom,"},{"time":849686,"text":"rather than a force which will hiddenly manipulate us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":854432,"text":"Right now, many of us"},{"time":857025,"text":"do not even know that the fight is going on,"},{"time":859778,"text":"but it is, whether you like it or not."},{"time":862450,"text":"And at the risk of playing the serpent,"},{"time":865254,"text":"I will tell you that the tools for the fight"},{"time":868151,"text":"are here, the awareness of what is going on,"},{"time":871160,"text":"and in your hands,"},{"time":872515,"text":"just a few clicks away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":876255,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":877737,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}